      <title>咆哮的小猫让 Chewy 和 Petco 的股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/roaring-kitty-sends-chewy-petco-stocks-soaring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chewy 和 Petco 的股价在 Keith Gill（网上以“咆哮的小猫”著称）发布关于 X of a dog 的表情包后飙升。涨势很短暂，这两只股票当天收盘均下跌。彭博社的 Abigail Doolittle 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/roaring-kitty-sends-chewy-petco-stocks-soaring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 20:16:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Chewy 和 Petco 分享“咆哮的小猫”发布的狗狗图片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/chewy-chwy-petco-woof-soar-as-roaring-kitty-posts-dog-image-on-x</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，在网名“咆哮的小猫”基思·吉尔 (Keith Gill) 在 X 上发布了一张卡通狗的图片后，Chewy Inc. 和 Petco Health and Wellness Co. 的股价一度飙升，但随后又迅速下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/chewy-chwy-petco-woof-soar-as-roaring-kitty-posts-dog-image-on-x</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 17:48:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
